| CVE | Severity | Package | Affected Images | Fix Version |
|-----|----------|---------|----------------|-------------|
| `CVE-2024-41110` | 🔴 Critical | `github.com/docker/docker` | `quay.io/prometheus/prometheus:v2.44.0` | `docker v23.0.15` |
| `CVE-2024-41110` | 🔴 Critical | `github.com/docker/docker` | `quay.io/prometheus/prometheus:v2.46.0` | `docker v25.0.6` |
| `CVE-2024-2961` | 🔴 Critical | `libc6` | `ghcr.io/peimanaja/artifactory_exporter:v1.9.3` | Base image rebuild ⚠️ |
 
> ⚠️ **Note:** `CVE-2024-2961` on the `artifactory_exporter` image is **NOT fixed** by this chart upgrade. It requires a separate base image rebuild.
 
